Class ForwardResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.forms.html.ForwardResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FormResult

    public class ForwardResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements FormResult
    FormResult to indicate forwarding to a page from within a servlet. From a transition the current target/provider will be passed by attribute by default. Optionally additional attributes can be supplied by this class.
